        <Parent_String>plows (agricultural equipment) [300233317], agricultural equipment [300233315], equipment by process [300024659], equipment [300122241], Tools and Equipment (hierarchy name) [300022238], Furnishings and Equipment (hierarchy name) [300264551], Objects Facet [300264092]</Parent_String>
